{"validation_override": true, "owner_org": "9391E0A2-9717-4755-B548-4499C21F917B", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "N66d38mW092d49m_1", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\u00e9o", "title_fra": "Base de donn\u00e9es des points d'appui au sol, Canada - N66d38mW092d49m_1", "keywords": "Geomatics,Geographic data,Photography,Aerial photography,Imagery and basemaps,Gcp,Air photo,Ground control points,Nts 56k10", "data_series_issue_identification": "N66d38mW092d49m_1", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "Base de donn\u00e9es des points d'appui au sol, Canada", "spatial_representation_type": "Grid | Grille", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "As Needed | Au besoin", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "geoginfo@NRCan.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "La Base de donn\u00e9es des points d'appui au sol (BDPAS) est une collection d'orthophotographies (ou chips) destin\u00e9e aux utilisateurs de SIG et de t\u00e9l\u00e9d\u00e9tection. La base de donn\u00e9es fournit une information utile et exacte \u00e9tablie \u00e0 partir de photos a\u00e9riennes corrig\u00e9es. L'utilisateur final peut s'y reporter \u00e0 titre de source de donn\u00e9es fondamentales pour corriger et valider les donn\u00e9es satellitaires, vectorielles et matricielles, pour fins de correction et de mise \u00e0 jour des cartes ainsi que d'analyse, de mod\u00e9lisation et de traitement des images. La BDPAS a d'abord \u00e9t\u00e9 constitu\u00e9e pour suppl\u00e9er au traitement et/ou \u00e0 la correction des donn\u00e9es LANDSAT et SPOT afin d'offrir des produits d'imagerie satellitaire \u00e0 valeur ajout\u00e9e. G\u00e9ogratis offre maintenant \u00e0 l'utilisateur final la possibilit\u00e9 d'acc\u00e9der \u00e0 ces donn\u00e9es en ligne de mani\u00e8re efficace et \u00e9conomique.", "id": "003bce71-38ee-5d2a-9288-936c40b5b90b", "presentation_form": "Image Digital | Image num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[66.600083, -92.743904], [66.618652, -92.743713], [66.618572, -92.698552], [66.600003, -92.698778], [66.600083, -92.743904]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.gtif", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.tfw", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.tif", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.summary", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}], "browse_graphic_url": "http://www.fakeimageurl123.com/foo.jpg", "topic_category": "Location  Localisation", "tags": [], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "1983-08-03", "time_period_coverage_start": "", "data_series_name": "Ground Control Database, Canada", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "", "notes": "The Ground Control Database (GCDB) is a collection of geo-corrected aerial photo images (or chips) developed for the GIS and remote sensing community. The database provides accurate and useful information obtained from corrected aerial photos. This database can be used by the end-user as a fundamental data source for correction and validation of satellite, vector and raster data, as well as for map correcting and updating, analysis, modeling, and image processing. The GCDB was initially developed to supplement processing and/or correction of LANDSAT and SPOT data for value added satellite imagery products. Now, through GeoGratis, online access to the GCDB is offered as an effi